---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Daily Programming - Kalthoff Performance">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">Daily Programming</h1>
      
      <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] mb-12 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517836357463-d25dfeac3438?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" 
          alt="Person performing daily workout routine" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          A structured long-term training plan is essential for sustainable health and performance. My remote training programs are designed to provide clear, progressive workouts, that give clients simultaneous freedom and structure to complete their plan. Using periodization strategies, each program includes structured strength and conditioning work, recovery techniques, and mobility exercises tailored to the individual's goals. With a focus on consistency and adaptability, my training plans help clients develop strength, resilience, and long-term progress on their own schedule.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What's Included</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Customized daily training programs based on your goals and schedule</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Periodized training plans for optimal progress</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Recovery and mobility protocols</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Regular program adjustments based on progress and feedback</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Program Delivery</h2>
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Powered by TeamBuildr</h3>
          <img src="/images/full-logo-white-orange.png" alt="TeamBuildr Logo" class="h-12 mb-6" />
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            All programming is delivered through TeamBuildr, a professional training app that provides:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 mt-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Easy-to-follow workout instructions with video demonstrations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Progress tracking and performance metrics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Direct communication with your coach</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Who Is This For?</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Individuals seeking structured, progressive training</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Busy professionals looking for flexible training options</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Anyone committed to long-term health and fitness</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-8 border border-white/10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Start Your Fitness Journey?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Take the first step towards your fitness goals with our expert daily programming.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-gray-200 transition duration-300">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 